      <title>C&#43;&#43;连接mysql</title>
      <link>https://kaikaixixi.xyz/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/c&#43;&#43;%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5mysql/</link>
